miracles : the holiday album is the first holiday album by saxophonist kenny g. it was released by arista records in 1994 , and peaked at number 1 on the billboard 200 , contemporary jazz albums and r&b/hip - hop albums charts.[ charts & awards ] at allmusic    it was the overall best - selling christmas/holiday album in the united states for both 1994 and 1996 .

holiday albums : this saxophonist 's " miracles : the holiday album " is said to be the bestselling christmas album of all time

